  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="my-4">Session Interest
      <small>Survey</small>
    </h1>

    <p>Please take a moment to help us schedule our rooms for CodeMash 2019. Take a moment and complete the following form based on the sessions you 
      think you are most likely to attend. This is not a popularity contest, and the speaker doesn't win anything for getting the most votes. All it
      does is help us gain an idea of where to put which session within the conference center.</p>
    <p>Also, this does not commit you to going to a particular session... you are free to change your mind. Thanks for your help!</p>
    
    <form action="/votes/vote" id="votingform" method="post">


      <div class="form-horizontal col-lg-12">
        <ul class="nav nav-tabs" id="mainTabs" role="tablist">
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link active" id="pg" data-toggle="tab" href="#precompilers" role="tab">Step 1: Pre-Compilers <span id="pcCount" class="badge badge-primary label-as-badge">0/4</span></a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" id="rg" data-toggle="tab" href="#regularsessions" role="tab">Step 2: Regular Sessions <span id="regCount" class="badge badge-primary label-as-badge">0/15</span></a>
          </li>
          <li class="nav-item">
            <a class="nav-link" id="vt" data-toggle="tab" href="#vote" role="tab">Step 3: Cast your vote</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <div id="mainContent" class="tab-content">
          <div id="precompilers" class="tab-pane active">

          </div>
          <div id="regularsessions" class="tab-pane">
          </div>
          <div id="vote" class="tab-pane">
            <p style="margin: 30px;">OK! You are ready to cast your vote for sessions. Press the button below to finish.</p>
            <div class="form-group" style="padding-bottom: 30px;">
              <div class="col-md-offset-2 col-md-10">
                <input type="submit" value="Cast Vote" class="btn btn-primary" />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="progress" style="width:100%; text-align:center; padding-top: 30px; padding-bottom: 30px;">
        <img src="img/download.gif">
      </div>

      <!-- Modal -->
      <div class="modal fade" id="precompModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
          <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header card-header bg-danger">
              <h5 class="modal-title">Ooops!</h5>
              <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
              </button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body card-body">
              You can only select four (4) pre-compilier sessions. You will need to deselect some before you can
              submit your vote.
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="modal fade" id="regularModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
          <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header card-header bg-danger">
              <h5 class="modal-title">Ooops!</h5>
              <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
              </button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body card-body">
              You can only select fifteen (15) regular sessions. You will need to deselect some before you can 
              submit your vote.
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="modal fade" id="successModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog">
          <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header card-header bg-success">
              <h5 class="modal-title">Thanks!</h5>
              <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
              </button>              
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body card-body">
              Your votes have been successfully recorded. Thanks for taking the time to help
              CodeMash be awesome!
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>

